version_description: This is a great and funny song to learn for the festive season, but I noticed other versions have this down in the key of Eb or D. I've transposed it for the key of C to make all the chords easy to play and give you deeper bass notes. All you have to do is stick a capo on the 3rd fret and you'll be playing in Eb just like The Killers. This version is also the only one with the diminished and 6ths chords included. Merry playing.

song_name: Have All The Songs Been Written
